  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "高校卒業前の1年間をクラブ活動やデートに費やしましょう。アルバイトをすることで、新しい服や化粧品を購入し、さまざまなおしゃれなアクティビティを楽しむことができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The second in the Kisekae series! This time, the contents include all fashionable items, including accessories and hair arrangements. You can get various types of clothes such as casual, street, and romantic, and you can combine them freely. Of course, special clothes are also available! In addition to face makeup, pierced earrings, rings, cuticles, etc. have also appeared, and hair can be arranged at the beauty salon. Six boys and four girls will appear, and the drama will develop in a fun high school life. Various events such as clubs and school events occur.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
